            }}></path></svg></a>{`Why is my liquidity worth less than I put in?`}</h2>
      <p>{`To understand why the value of a liquidity provider’s stake can go down despite income from fees, we need to look a bit more closely at the formula used by Kwikswap to govern trading. The formula really is very simple. If we neglect trading fees, we have the following:`}</p>
